      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JALAPENO POPPER (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (30.39) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. BELLA MATILDA (8) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5.5 lengths into third (24.23) at this track in a Grade 5 over 407m. Expected to feature. TOUGH ONE (5) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Below best last time at this track (30.75) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length sixth. Can feature with the right run. SUNBURNT DAWN (1) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into second last time out (24.12) over 407m at this track. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw.",
